<h2 id="copy-rules">Copy Rules</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Use the imperative voice for radio button labels.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Do not use terminal punctuation for radio button labels.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Maintain parallel construction for lists of related radio button labels.</p>
  </li>
</ul>
